Well, there's a lot of junk in his system
for such an old man.

01:23:20.371 --> 01:23:22.288
Apparently he was addicted to morphine.

01:23:22.373 --> 01:23:25.583
He tried to kick that
and he got readdicted to methadone.

01:23:25.668 --> 01:23:28.628
- Is he gonna be okay?
- We'll do our best.

01:23:33.300 --> 01:23:37.387
- Hi, Lillian.
- Hi, Ed. He's got a lot of visitors today.

01:23:37.471 --> 01:23:38.263
He does?

01:23:39.848 --> 01:23:41.265
Smile. That's it!

01:23:41.350 --> 01:23:43.267
- Hey! Hey!
- One more picture, sir?

01:23:43.352 --> 01:23:45.186
Do the doctors say
you're gonna get outta here?

01:23:45.270 --> 01:23:46.312
Freaks!

01:23:46.397 --> 01:23:48.523
Get outta here! Get outta here!

01:23:48.607 --> 01:23:51.526
What is wrong with you people?
Come on, trash barrel!

01:23:51.610 --> 01:23:53.569
Hey!

01:23:53.654 --> 01:23:55.571
Bela, what happened?

01:23:55.656 --> 01:23:58.282
Eddie, why did you chase them?

01:23:58.367 --> 01:24:02.620
After all these years,
the press is finally interested again in Bela Lugosi.

01:24:03.288 --> 01:24:04.706
Bela,

01:24:04.790 --> 01:24:08.334
those people are parasites,
they just wanna exploit you.

01:24:08.627 --> 01:24:11.379
Fine. Let them.

01:24:11.755 --> 01:24:14.382
There is no such thing
as bad press, Eddie.

01:24:14.466 --> 01:24:19.178
Man from New York even said
he's putting me on the front page.

01:24:20.514 --> 01:24:23.143
First celebrity ever to check into rehab.

01:24:26.520 --> 01:24:29.313
When I get out of here

01:24:29.565 --> 01:24:31.315
I will be healthy,

01:24:31.400 --> 01:24:33.484
strong,

01:24:33.736 --> 01:24:35.820
primed for my comeback...

01:24:48.083 --> 01:24:50.001
Hello again.

01:24:50.085 --> 01:24:52.462
- Hi.
- You look beat.

01:24:52.546 --> 01:24:55.339
No, I'm fine. How's your father?

01:24:55.966 --> 01:24:58.926
Better. Thank you for asking.
And your friend?

01:25:01.813 --> 01:25:03.014
Not good.

01:25:04.683 --> 01:25:08.686
Well, I made him some booties
to cheer him up.

01:25:10.606 --> 01:25:13.524
They're black, to match his cape.

01:25:17.279 --> 01:25:20.198
Say, have you always
lived in Los Angeles?

01:25:20.324 --> 01:25:22.909
No, I'm from back east.
Poughkeepsie.

01:25:22.993 --> 01:25:26.996
You know, all-American small town,
everybody knows everybody,

01:25:27.080 --> 01:25:29.999
my dad worked for the post office,
I was a Boy Scout.

01:25:30.083 --> 01:25:32.877
- Did you find it boring?
- No, not at all.

01:25:32.961 --> 01:25:35.004
I had my comic books and pulp magazines.

01:25:35.088 --> 01:25:37.048
Used to listen to radio dramas constantly.

01:25:37.132 --> 01:25:38.174
I love those shows.

01:25:38.258 --> 01:25:40.218
- <i>The Shadow, Inner Sanctum.</i>
- Yes.

01:25:40.594 --> 01:25:42.136
And <i>The Mercury Theater</i>
with Orson Welles.

01:25:43.639 --> 01:25:46.390
Boy, you know, every Saturday afternoon
me and my dad

01:25:46.475 --> 01:25:49.393
marched down the street in our uniform
to the little movie theater.

01:25:50.020 --> 01:25:51.562
Oh, the spook house!

01:26:27.474 --> 01:26:30.268
You're not gonna believe
the first picture I ever saw.

01:26:30.519 --> 01:26:32.311
It was your friend's... <i>Dracula.</i>

01:26:32.396 --> 01:26:34.981
That's incredible,
that's the first picture I ever saw.

01:26:35.065 --> 01:26:36.357
That is incredible.

01:26:36.441 --> 01:26:38.860
You know, I had to sleep
with the lights on for a week.

01:26:38.944 --> 01:26:40.361
I had to for a month.

01:26:40.445 --> 01:26:43.114
But I never missed a Lugosi picture
after that one.

01:26:44.533 --> 01:26:47.869
A few years ago I actually saw him
do <i>Dracula</i> live.

01:26:47.953 --> 01:26:49.912
It was much scarier in person.

01:26:52.457 --> 01:26:54.625
Oh. We're stuck.

01:27:02.384 --> 01:27:04.135
Kathy,

01:27:05.721 --> 01:27:09.432
I'm about to tell you something that
I never told any girl on a first date.

01:27:11.560 --> 01:27:14.478
But I think it's important that you know

01:27:21.028 --> 01:27:23.070
I like to wear women's clothes.

01:27:25.866 --> 01:27:29.035
- Huh?
- I like to wear women's clothes.

01:27:30.287 --> 01:27:33.247
Panties, brassieres, sweaters, pumps.

01:27:34.333 --> 01:27:36.709
It's just something I do.

01:27:36.793 --> 01:27:40.755
Yes, I can't believe I'm telling you this,
but I really like you

01:27:40.839 --> 01:27:44.592
and I don't want it getting
in the way down the road.

01:27:44.676 --> 01:27:48.763
Does this mean
you don't like sex with girls?

01:27:48.847 --> 01:27:51.390
No, I love sex with girls.

01:27:57.731 --> 01:27:59.690
Okay.

01:28:01.318 --> 01:28:02.401
Okay?

01:28:04.863 --> 01:28:06.989
Okay.

01:28:18.001 --> 01:28:22.338
You see, we thought that Mr. Lugosi
was insured through his union.

01:28:22.422 --> 01:28:23.798
Isn't he?

01:28:23.882 --> 01:28:26.634
No, they say his eligibility
ran out years ago.

01:28:30.055 --> 01:28:31.973
Look, Doctor,

01:28:32.057 --> 01:28:34.558
