01:32:33.006 --> 01:32:34.340
- I can't see!
- Get off me!

01:32:34.424 --> 01:32:35.549
Let's go!

01:32:35.634 --> 01:32:36.853
I gotta save 'em!

01:32:39.137 --> 01:32:40.554
Get your heads down!

01:32:40.639 --> 01:32:42.765
Come on, let's go!
We're getting the heck outta here!

01:32:43.849 --> 01:32:45.226
Can't see!

01:32:45.310 --> 01:32:48.062
I can't see anymore!

01:32:53.276 --> 01:32:56.028
Hey, come on! Let's split!

01:33:04.162 --> 01:33:05.256
Taxi!

01:33:07.040 --> 01:33:08.082
Stop!

01:33:08.166 --> 01:33:10.251
Get in! Come on!
Go on, get in!

01:33:20.011 --> 01:33:22.513
Now, that was a premiere.

01:33:31.189 --> 01:33:33.107
Eddie,

01:33:33.191 --> 01:33:34.859
