01:40:12.465 --> 01:40:16.677
Well, Ed, I was thinkin' like
when Bela played Fu Manchu.

01:40:16.761 --> 01:40:19.137
- Paul, that was Karloff.
- Oh.

01:40:19.222 --> 01:40:21.181
- You're gonna have to try harder.
- Okay.

01:40:21.265 --> 01:40:23.350
- Try to be a cut above. Go get 'em.
- Okay. Right.

01:40:23.434 --> 01:40:24.071
Keep Sunday open,

01:40:24.110 --> 01:40:27.021
- the producers want us to get baptized.
- Okay.

01:40:33.152 --> 01:40:37.197
You know, hon, when you rewrite a script,
it just gets better and better.

01:40:38.449 --> 01:40:42.119
