I brought the script.
You'll be portraying the ghoul's wife.

01:41:00.638 --> 01:41:03.390
- The ghoul's wife?
- Yes.

01:41:04.474 --> 01:41:06.184
You should feel lucky.

01:41:06.269 --> 01:41:08.895
Eddie's the only fella in town
who doesn't pass judgment on people.

01:41:08.980 --> 01:41:12.482
That's right. If I did,
I wouldn't have any friends.

01:41:12.900 --> 01:41:16.820
Look, would it be possible to make
the ghoul's wife a little less prominent

01:41:16.904 --> 01:41:18.280
so people wouldn't really
notice me in the movie?

01:41:18.364 --> 01:41:19.906
You don't want to be noticed?

01:41:19.991 --> 01:41:24.244
Yeah. How about this? What if I don't
have any lines? I'll play the part mute.

01:41:24.328 --> 01:41:26.788
- Mute?
- Hey, it's Dr. Tom.

01:41:26.873 --> 01:41:29.583
- Dr. Tom! Hiya!
