Now, here, let me fix that.

01:41:55.526 --> 01:41:57.194
My gosh!

01:41:58.863 --> 01:42:00.822
Don't move.

01:42:04.285 --> 01:42:06.578
It's uncanny.

01:42:07.955 --> 01:42:11.041
Look at his head! It's uncanny!

01:42:14.420 --> 01:42:16.797
<i>Lift up your voice</i>

01:42:16.881 --> 01:42:19.674
<i>And let us sing</i>

01:42:19.759 --> 01:42:24.387
<i>Alleluia, alleluia</i>

